ZH: 亲爱的，你吃过饭了吗？
EN: Dear, have you eaten yet?

ZH: 亲戚们都来了，我们准备开饭了。
EN: All the relatives are here, we are ready to start the meal.

ZH: 亲眼见证了这个奇迹，我感到很荣幸。
EN: I am honored to witness this miracle with my own eyes.

ZH: 亲爱的，我爱你。
EN: Darling, I love you.

ZH: 亲手制作的礼物总是最贴心的。
EN: Handmade gifts are always the most thoughtful.

ZH: 亲自动手才能领会真正的乐趣。
EN: Only by doing it ourselves can we truly understand the joy.

ZH: 亲身经历才能了解其中的辛酸。
EN: Only by experiencing it ourselves can we understand the bitterness in it.

ZH: 亲近自然，远离喧嚣。
EN: Get close to nature and stay away from the hustle and bustle.

ZH: 亲自亲历的经历是最珍贵的财富。
EN: Personal experiences are the most precious wealth.

ZH: 亲友团的支持是最重要的力量。
EN: The support of friends and family is the most important strength.

ZH: 亲密的朋友永远是你最大的财富。
EN: Close friends are always your greatest treasure.

ZH: 亲密关系需要彼此尊重和信任。
EN: Intimate relationships require mutual respect and trust.

ZH: 亲情是永恒不变的主题。
EN: Family love is an eternal theme.

ZH: 亲手放置的花朵最美丽。
EN: The flowers placed by hand are the most beautiful.

ZH: 亲手料理美食，满足心灵的味蕾。
EN: Cook food with your own hands, satisfy the taste buds of the soul.

ZH: 亲自前往，见证历史的发展。
EN: Go there in person, witness the development of history.

ZH: 亲切的笑容温暖了我的心房。
EN: The warm smile warmed my heart.

ZH: 亲友们纷纷表示祝贺。
EN: Friends and family expressed their congratulations one after another.

ZH: 亲身经历才能感受到生活的酸甜苦辣。
EN: Only personal experience can feel the ups and downs of life.

ZH: 亲近大自然，保护环境是我们每个人的责任。
EN: Get closer to nature, protecting the environment is the responsibility of each and everyone.
